'Yan Majalisar Dokokin Wales sun yi ta tsoron yin rikici da 'yan Muppets
Wasu 'yan majalisar sun yi mamaki da shawarar canja sunayensu zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament, Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Dalilin shi ne, akwai shirin canja sunan Majalisar ta Duniya zuwa 'Welsh Parliament' (Paramandan Wales).
'Yan majalisa na dukan bangarorin siyasa suna tsoron zama abin zargi.
Wani dan majalisar dokokin kasar na jam'iyyar Labour ya ce kungiyarsa ta damu da yadda sunan Twp da Pwp suka yi magana.
Ga masu karatu da ba Welsh ba: A Welsh, twp yana nufin doof da pwp yana nufin Aa.
Wani dan majalisar dokokin kasar na jam'iyyar Plaid Cymru ya ce dukan kungiyar ba ta farin ciki kuma ya ba da shawarwari na madadin.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Welsh Conservative Party ya ce kungiyarsa ta yi murna da sauya sunansa, amma ya nuna cewa akwai kamanceceniya tsakanin MWP da Muppet.
A wannan yanayin, ana furta haruffan Welsh w kamar haruffan u a Turanci da ake magana a Yorkshire.
Hukumar Majalisar (Kungiyar Majalisar Kasa) da ke tsara dokar canja sunaye a yanzu ta ce: Sai 'yan majalisar suka yanke shawara game da sunayen da za a ba 'yan majalisar.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba da izinin Majalisar Dokokin Wales ta canza sunanta.
A watan Yuni, kwamitin ya wallafa sakamakon sauraron da aka yi a fili game da shawarwarin da suka nuna goyon baya ga sunan Welsh Parliament ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya.
Game da sunayen 'yan majalisar, kwamitin ya fi son 'yan majalisar Welsh Parliament' (Welsh Parliament members) ko 'yan majalisar Welsh MPs' (WMPs) yayin da a sauraron jama'a, zabin 'MWP' ya sami mafi yawan goyon baya.
Da alama 'yan majalisar sun gabatar da wasu zaɓuɓɓuka, amma neman yarjejeniya na iya zama matsala ga shugaban kasa Elin Jones, wanda za a gabatar da doka a cikin makonni.
Dokar gyara za ta ƙara ɗauke da wasu canje-canje ga yadda majalisar ta ke aiki, ciki har da dokoki game da hana 'yan majalisar da kuma tsarin kwamitocin.
A lokacin da suke tattaunawa game da dokar, 'yan majalisar za su iya yin zabe a kan sunayensu.
