Mutane fiye da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron Brett Kavanaugh
Mutane fiye da miliyan 20 sun kalli labarai masu ban sha'awa da aka yi a gidan talabijin guda shida a ranar Alhamis, na Brett Kavanaugh da kuma matarsa Christine Blasey Ford da suka zarge shi da yin lalata da shi a shekarun 1980.
A halin yanzu, halin da ake ciki a siyasa ya ci gaba, kuma a ranar Juma'a, tashoshin talabijin sun dakatar da shirye-shiryen su na yau da kullum saboda wani juyi na minti na ƙarshe: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi, wanda ya ba da umurni ga FBI ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda game da zargin.
Ford ya shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai cewa ya tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya sha giya a wani biki na makarantar sakandare, ya matsa mata kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin cire tufafinta.
Kavanaugh ya ce a wata sanarwa mai cike da sha'awa, ya tabbata cewa ba haka ba ne ya faru.
Akwai yiwuwar fiye da masu kallo miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ta ruwaito sun kalli sauraron.
Kamfanin ya gano yawan masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ga sauran cibiyoyin sadarwa kamar su PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network da suka yi sauraron karar, ba a nan take ba.
Bugu da ƙari, Nielsen yawanci yana da matsala wajen auna yawan masu kallo a ofisoshinsa.
Don yin la'akari da wannan, wannan ya yi daidai da yawan masu kallo a wasan wasan kwallon kafa na wasan kwaikwayo ko kuma kyautar Oscar.
Kafofin watsa labarai na Fox News Channel, wanda masu gabatar da shirye-shiryensa na ra'ayi suna goyon bayan Kavanaugh sosai, sun rubuta mafi yawan adadin masu sauraro na dukan rana, a cewar Nielsen, tare da masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a matsakaici.
ABC ta zo na biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
Nielsen ya nuna cewa CBS ta samu masu kallo miliyan 3.1 da NBC miliyan 2.94 da MSNBC miliyan 2.89 da CNN miliyan 2.52.
Bayan sauraron, mutane sun yi murna sosai.
Flake shi ne babban mutum a wasan kwaikwayon na Juma'a.
Bayan da ofishin dan jam'iyyar Republican mai tawali'u ya fitar da wata sanarwa cewa zai yi zabe a madadin Kavanaugh, a safiyar Juma'a, kyamarorin CNN da CBS sun kama shi yana kallon masu zanga-zangar suna ta matsa masa da murya a cikin lif a kan hanyar zuwa gaban kwamitin shari'a.
Ya yi ta kallon ƙasa na minti daya yayin da ake masa horo. An watsa wannan hoton a CNN.
