Rikicin 'yan sanda da 'yan tsattsage na Catalonia a gaban ranar tunawa da zaben samun 'yancin kai
A Barcelona, an kama mutane shida a ranar Asabar bayan rikici tsakanin 'yan sanda da masu zanga-zangar neman 'yancin kai. Dubban mutane sun halarci wasu zanga-zangar don tunawa da ranar farko ta raba gardama a Catalonia.
Wasu 'yan ta'adda da suka yi wa juna baya a rufe sun yi wa 'yan sanda ja-gora kuma suka yi musu iska da kuma yin amfani da foda don su sa iska ta yi duhu a kan tituna da yawanci masu yawon bude ido suke.
A cikin yini, an yi ta yin tawaye da 'yan sanda, waɗanda suka yi amfani da sandunansu don su hana faɗa.
Ƙungiyoyin 'yancin kai sun yi wa'azi na sa'o'i da yawa suna ihu suna cewa, "Babu wani abu da za a manta da shi, ba wani abu da za a gafarta masa ba", yayin da 'yan ƙungiyar suka yi musu hamayya suna cewa, "Bari ƙasar Spain ta daɗe".
Kamar yadda manema labarai na yankin suka ruwaito, an yi wa mutane goma sha huɗu magani domin ƙananan raunuka da suka sha a lokacin zanga-zangar.
Shekara guda bayan zaben raba gardama na 1 ga watan Oktoba, wanda Madrid ta ce ba bisa doka ba ne amma Catalans masu rabuwa suka yi bikin, har yanzu halin da ake ciki a yankin na 'yancin kai yana da matukar tashin hankali.
