A ranar Asabar, hukumomi sun ce an kashe mutane akalla 384, da yawa daga cikinsu sun yi fama da ruwa a lokacin da wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi da tsunami suka yi a tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia suka yi wa raƙuman ruwa masu yawa.
A ranar Juma'a, daruruwan mutane sun taru a wani biki a bakin rairayin bakin teku a birnin Palu, inda a lokacin da duhu ya yi duhu, raƙuman ruwa masu tsayi na mita shida suka yi ta kaiwa ga bakin rairayin bakin teku, suna kashe mutane da yawa kuma suna lalata duk abin da ya hana su yin hakan.
Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta riga ta faru kafin tsunami.
Lokacin da ake fuskantar barazanar tsunami a jiya, mutane suna kan rairayin bakin teku suna bin ayyukansu ba tare da gudu ba, kuma sun zama wadanda suka yi wa barazanar ba, in ji Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, kakakin hukumar hana bala'i ta BNPB a wani taro a Jakarta.
Tsunami ba shi kaɗai ya faru ba, ya halaka motoci, bishiyoyi da gidaje, ya kai ga komai a ƙasa, in ji Nugroho. Ya kara da cewa tsunami ya hau kan teku da saurin mil 800 a kowace awa kafin ya kai ga bakin teku.
Ya ce wasu mutane sun hau itatuwa suna tserewa tsunami kuma sun tsira.
