AMLO ta Mexico ta yi alkawarin ba za ta yi amfani da sojoji a kan fararen hula ba
Zababben shugaban kasar Mexico Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin kada ya yi amfani da karfi na soja a kan fararen hula yayin da ake cika shekaru 50 da zubar da jini a kan ɗaliban da ke kasarsa.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawari a Tlatelolco Plaza a ranar Asabar cewa ba zai taɓa amfani da sojoji don zaluntar mutanen Mexico ba.
A ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 1968, sojoji sun harba wani zanga-zanga a filin wasa, inda suka kashe mutane 300. A wannan lokacin, ƙungiyoyin ɗalibai na hagu suna kafa kansu a duk Latin Amurka.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin tallafawa matasa na Mexico ta hanyar ba da tallafin kowane wata ga dalibai da kuma buɗe wasu jami'o'in gwamnati kyauta.
Ya ce rashin aikin yi da rashin samun damar yin horo suna kai wa matasa ga yin laifi.
Ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da ake kashewa a kan fasaha ta wucin gadi
Da yake kasar Sin ta ƙara yin amfani da fasaha ta wucin gadi, ya kamata Amurka ta ninka yawan kuɗin da ta kashe a kan bincike a wannan fannin, in ji mai saka jari da kuma mai ba da shawara kan fasaha ta wucin gadi Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Wannan bayani ya biyo bayan sanarwar AI da wasu bangarori na gwamnatin Amurka suka yi, ko da yake Amurka ba ta da wata dabarar AI.
A halin yanzu, a shekarar da ta gabata, kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirin ta na zama kasa ta farko a fannin kera kere ta AI nan da shekarar 2030.
"Binciken AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa idan aka yi la'akari da cewa sauran ƙasashe suna da nisa a baya na Amurka. Muna neman sabon ci gaban AI", in ji Lee.
Da ninki biyu na kudaden zai iya ninka damar samun babban nasarar AI na gaba a Amurka, Lee ya ce a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order  aka buga a wannan watan ta Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI a kasar Sin, Face++.
A shekarun 1980, ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon a kan tsarin AI wanda ya ci nasara a kan mafi yawan 'yan wasan Othello na Amurka. Daga baya ya zama babban jami'in bincike na Microsoft da shugaban kamfanin Google a China.
Lee ya yaba da gasar fasaha ta gwamnatin Amurka kamar ta Robotics Challenge na Hukumar Kula da Ci Gaban Ci Gaban (DARPA) kuma ya tambayi lokacin gasar ta gaba domin yana son taimakawa wajen gano masu hangen nesa na gaba.
Lee ya ce masu bincike a Amirka suna bukatar su yi aiki tuƙuru don su samu tallafin gwamnati.
"Ba kasar Sin ce ke karbar manyan jami'ai ba, amma kamfanoni ne", in ji Lee.
A cikin 'yan shekarun nan, Facebook da Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun kori jami'o'i da yawa da ke aiki a kan fasaha ta AI.
Lee ya ce, sauya manufofin baƙi na Amurka zai iya taimaka wa kokarin AI na Amurka.
Ya ce: "Ina ganin ya kamata a ba da takardar shaidar da za ta taimaka wa masu samun digiri na biyu a fannin AI.
A watan Yuli na 2017, Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirin ci gaban fasahar Artificial Intelligence na gaba.
A cewar Lee, National Natural Science Foundation of China tana ba da kudi ga cibiyoyin ilimi kamar National Science Foundation da sauran kungiyoyin gwamnati, amma ingancin aikin ilimi a kasar Sin ya ragu.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Artificial Intelligence ta Ƙungiya, wadda za ta haɗa masana'antu da masana kimiyya da kuma fadar White House ta sanar da kafa kwamitin musamman na Artificial Intelligence.
Bugu da ƙari, a wannan watan, DARPA ta sanar da zuba jari na dala biliyan 2 a cikin shirin AI Next.
A halin yanzu, Hukumar Kimiyya ta Kasa (NSF) tana zuba jari fiye da dala miliyan 100 a shekara don bincike na AI.
A halin yanzu, an shafe watanni ba a yi wani abu ba game da dokokin Amurka game da kafa Hukumar Tsaro ta Kasa a kan Ilimin Artificial.
'Yan Macedonia sun amince da sauya sunan ƙasarsu a cikin raba gardama
A ranar Lahadi, al'ummar Macedonia sun amince da zaben raba gardama na neman sauya sunan ƙasar zuwa Jamhuriyar Arewacin Macedonia, wanda zai kawo ƙarshen rikici da ya shafe shekaru da yawa da ake yi da Girka, wadda ta hana Macedonia shiga Tarayyar Turai da NATO.
Girka, wadda ke da lardin da ake kira Macedonia, ta ce sunan makwabcinta na arewa yana nufin cewa wannan ya ɗaukaka wannan da'awar zuwa yankin Girka. Saboda haka, Girka ta yi veto a kan shigar da Macedonia cikin NATO da EU.
