Tun shekara ta 2006, Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta amince da tsaurara takunkumi a kan Koriya ta Arewa don ta kashe shirin Pyongyang na makaman nukiliya da makaman nukiliya.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a kan iyakokin babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, sannan ya ce zai sake ziyarci Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron koli na biyu.
