Kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV ko AIDS ya karu da kashi 14 cikin 100.
Jami'an kiwon lafiya sun ce mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na shekara ta 2018 kadai, an samu sababbin mutane kusan 40,000.
