Menene bikin Global Citizen Festival kuma menene wannan bikin ya taimaka wajen rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar ne za a yi bikin Global Citizen a birnin New York, bikin kiɗa na shekara-shekara da ke nuna jerin taurari masu ban sha'awa da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa na yaki da talauci a duniya.
Dubban mutane za su halarci bikin Global Citizen, wanda za a yi a karo na bakwai a wannan shekara, ba don ganin abubuwan da Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes suka yi ba, amma don ƙara wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar taron: magance talauci mai tsanani har zuwa shekara ta 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen wanda aka fara yi a shekarar 2012 wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project. A cikin wannan aikin, wata kungiya ta duniya tana ƙoƙarin magance talauci ta hanyar motsa mutane da yawa su shiga cikin aikin.
Don samun tikitin kyauta don taron (wani zaɓi zai zama siyan tikitin VIP), dole ne mutum ya yi wasu ayyuka, kamar aikin sa kai, sadarwa tare da wani babban jami'in siyasa a duniya (ta hanyar imel ko waya) ko kuma irin waɗannan ayyukan don wayar da kan jama'a game da burin  yaki da talauci 
To, yaya wannan aikin yake, idan aka yi la'akari da cewa Global Citizen na da shekaru 12 kafin a cimma burin?
Shin tunanin yin wani babban kide kide kyauta wata hanya ce mai kyau ta tabbatar wa mutane cewa lokaci ya yi da za su yi wani abu, ko kuma wani abu ne da ake kira clicktivism  idan kana da ra'ayin yin wani abu ta hanyar sanya hannu kan wata takarda ta yanar gizo ko aikawa da tweet?
Kamfanin Global Citizen ya ce tun daga shekarar 2011, an yi wa wannan aikin fiye da miliyan 19 na tallafi kuma an cimma burin da ya dace.
An ce waɗannan ayyukan sun taimaka wajen sa manyan 'yan siyasa a duniya su sanar da alkawura da dabaru da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayuwar mutane biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta ambata alkawura da sanarwa 390 da suka fito daga ayyukanta, wanda aƙalla dala biliyan 10 na Amurka aka riga an biya ko kuma aka karɓa ta hanyar tara kuɗi.
A cewar ƙididdigar kungiyar, har zuwa yanzu, kudaden da aka tabbatar sun shafi kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition Project, wani hadin gwiwa na masu zuba jari da masu aiwatarwa da ke zaune a Burtaniya, wadanda suka yi alkawarin tallafawa yara a ci gaban su na musamman, kuma sun yi alkawarin bayar da dala miliyan 35 na taimakon Rwanda wajen yaki rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan sun samu fiye da 4,700 tweets daga Global Citizens.
Da taimakon gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin ƙasa, da kuma 'yan ƙasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya sa rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki ya zama tarihi, jakadan The Power of Nutrition, Tracey Ullman, ya gaya wa masu sauraro a wani taro na raye-raye a London a watan Afrilu na 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma sanar da cewa bayan fiye da ayyuka 5,000 da aka yi don kiran Birtaniya ta inganta yanayin abinci na iyaye mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da samun kuɗi don aikin The Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai ga mata da yara miliyan 5 da kuma samar da taimakon abinci.
