Wata mako bayan wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wata sanarwa a wata jaridar Amurka da ke nuna amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin ya zargi babban birnin kasar Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka don yin amfani da ita don yin amfani da ita.
A ranar Laraba ta gabata, Donald Trump ya yi magana ne game da takardar da aka biya na China Daily a cikin Des Moines Register, mujallar da ta fi sayarwa a Iowa, bayan ya zargi China da tsoma baki a zaben Amurka na ranar 6 ga Nuwamba, zargin da kasar Sin ta musanta.
zargin da Trump ya yi cewa Beijing ta yi kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya yi daidai da sanarwar da jami'an Amurka suka bayar ga Reuters, wani sabon mataki na karuwar yakin neman zabe da Washington ta kaddamar domin matsa lamba a kan kasar Sin.
Duk da yake gwamnatocin kasashen waje suna yin tallace-tallace don bunkasa tattalin arziki, Beijing da Washington suna cikin yakin cinikayya mai tsanani, tare da yin amfani da takunkumi a kan shigo da kayayyaki daga ƙasashen biyu.
Ya kamata harajin da kasar Sin ta yi a lokacin da aka fara yakin cinikayya ya shafi masu fitar da kaya a jihohi kamar Iowa da suka goyi bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana na kasar Sin da na Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, wanda ke fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin a manyan sikelin, ya ce Beijing ta yi wa ma'aikata, masu mallakar gona da kuma kamfanoni lahani.
A wani jawabi da Branstad ya bayar a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, kasar Sin ta yi ta ninka wannan zalunci ta hanyar yin tallan talla a cikin jaridarsu a Amurka.
Da yake yada labaransa, gwamnatin Sin ta ci gaba da yin amfani da al'adar da aka tabbatar a Amirka ta 'yancin yin magana da kuma kafafen yada labarai masu zaman kansu ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace da aka biya a cikin Des Moines Register, in ji Branstad.
A akasin haka, za ku ga wasu ƙididdigar rashin jituwa a cikin ƙauyuka a nan birnin Beijing, kuma ba za ku ga ainihin yadda ra'ayoyin da ke tsakanin 'yan kasar Sin game da ci gaban tattalin arzikin kasar Sin suke nunawa ba, tun da yake kafofin watsa labarai suna hannun jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin,  ya rubuta.
