Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo mai ban mamaki yana shirin kaddamar da wani sabon intanet don ya yi gwagwarmaya da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta duniya, yana gabatar da wani kamfani a kasuwa a yanzu, da nufin yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin da aka yi na wannan mashahurin mai fasaha, Inrupt, wani kamfani ne wanda ya dogara ne akan dandamali na Open Source Solid na Berners-Lee.
A cikin Solid, masu amfani za su iya zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma wanda zai iya samun damar yin amfani da wane bayani.
A wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya ce manufar da ke bayan Inrupt ita ce ta yi sarauta a duniya.
Ya ce, "Dole ne mu yi aiki yanzu".
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Wannan app ɗin yana amfani da fasahar Solid don masu amfani su iya ƙirƙirar bayanan sirri na kan layi ko POD.
Za ta iya samun jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyuka, kalandar, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa da kuma wasu kayan aiki don kamfanoni da masu zaman kansu.
Kamar Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack, da Spotify, duk abun cikin yana cikin burauzar guda kuma yana samuwa a lokaci guda.
Abu na musamman game da adana bayanan sirri a kan layi shi ne cewa mai amfani zai iya yanke shawara ko wane ne zai iya samun damar wane bayanai.
Kamfanin ya bayyana wannan ra'ayi a matsayin inganta mutum da kuma ci gaba ta hanyar bayanai.
Shugaban kamfanin John Bruce ya ce manufar Inrupt ita ce kamfanin ya yi amfani da albarkatu, matakai da kuma iyawa don sanya Solid a wurin kowa.
A halin yanzu, Berners-Lee, Bruce, da wasu masu ci gaba da aka yi amfani da su wajen yin wannan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shirye masu son kai.
Tun farkon wannan makon, masu bunkasa fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen kansu na rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya sanar da cewa shi da tawagarsa ba za su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba game da ko za a yi wani babban canji wanda zai sa a sake tsara dukkanin tsarin kasuwancin su cikin dare.
Ba mu nemi izinin su ba.
A wani rubutu da ya wallafa a kan Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa aikin Inrupt shi ne samar da samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu don kare mutunci da ingancin sabon yanar gizo mai tushe da ƙarfi.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya sake tsara Intanet sa'ad da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin da suka gabata, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai muhimmiyar rawa wajen tattauna batun tsaka tsaki a kan cibiyar sadarwa.
Ko da bayan Inrupt ya fara aiki, Berners-Lee ya ci gaba da kasancewa wanda ya kafa kuma ya zama darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation, da Open Data Institute.
Ya kara da cewa, "Ina da tabbaci sosai game da wannan sabon zamani na yanar gizo.
An girmama firist Bernard Vann, wanda ya ɗauki Gicciye na Victoria a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya
Firist na cocin Ingila ne kaɗai da aka ba kyautar Gicciye na Victoria a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya, kuma an yi masa hakan a garinsu bayan shekara 100.
Lt. Col. da Firist Bernard Vann sun sami lambar yabo saboda aikinsa a hari kan Bellenglise da Lehaucourt a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918.
Amma, bayan kwana huɗu, wani mai harbi ya kashe shi kuma bai san cewa ya sami lambar yabo mafi girma ta yaƙi ta Birtaniya ba.
A ranar Lahadi, jikokinsa biyu sun buɗe wani abin tunawa a wani biki a Rushden, Northamptonshire.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikoki, Michael Vann, ya ce wannan aikin yana da alama domin an bayyana dutsen tun shekara 100 bayan aikin jaruntakar da aka yi wa kakansa.
A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lt. Col. Vann ya jagoranci rundunarsa ta hanyar Canal de Saint-Quentin, ta hanyar hazo mai yawa da kuma harbi mai tsanani na bindigogi da bindigogi.
Daga baya, ya ci gaba da bin diddigin wuta kuma ya ci gaba da bin diddigin da ya fi ƙarfinsa kafin ya yi amfani da makami na soja a gabansa kuma ya kashe rukunonin soja uku.
An kashe Lt. Col. Vann a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918, ta hanyar wani dan wasan Jamus mai kaifin baki; dan kadan fiye da wata daya kafin ƙarshen yakin.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce ayyukan kakansa wani abu ne da bai taɓa yin adalci a kansa ba, kuma a lokaci guda, abin da ke sa mutum ya yi sanyin gwiwa.
Tare da ɗan'uwansa Dr. James Vann, ya sa kambi bayan bikin, a ƙarƙashin jagorancin Brentwood Imperial Youth Band.
Michael Vann ya ce yana jin daɗin halartar bikin, kuma ya kara da cewa ƙarfin hali na wani jarumi na gaske ya bayyana ne ta hanyar goyon bayan mutane da yawa.
