An zargi dan wasan da ke buga wa tawagar Portugal da Juventus Turin da yin fyade da wata 'yar Amirka mai suna Kathryn Mayorga a wani otal a Las Vegas a shekarar 2009.
An ce daga baya ya biya ta dala 375,000 don ta daina yin shiru game da abin da ya faru, in ji Jaridar Der Spiegel a ranar Juma'a.
A wani bidiyo na Instagram na rayuwa da yake da mabiya miliyan 142, Ronaldo mai shekara 33 ya kira rahoton "Fake News" sa'o'i kadan bayan an wallafa shi.
"A'a, ba a yi ba.
Abin da suka ruwaito a yau: Labaran karya ne, "in ji wanda ya lashe kyautar Ballon d'Or sau biyar a gaban kyamarar.
Kuna son ku yi amfani da sunana don ku nuna kanku.
Wannan al'ada ce.
