Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne aka kashe a wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na ƙasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kamar yadda hukumomi suka ce.
Saboda rashin amfani da hanyoyin sadarwa, jami'an tsaro sun kasa samun bayanai daga gundumar Donggala, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu, wanda ke kusa da tsakiyar girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga birnin Palu bayan da aka yi wannan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya ne kuma yana kan iyakar bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da kimanin mutane 379,800 a cikin 2017.
A lokacin da aka yi girgizar ƙasa da tsunami, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da haihuwa.
Donggala wani yanki ne na jihar Sulawesi da ke arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda ke da tsawon kilomita 300 a bakin teku.
A shekara ta 2017, an kiyasta cewa mutane 299,200 ne ke zaune a gundumar, wata hukuma mai kula da yankin.
Fishing da kuma noma sune manyan hanyoyin samun kudin shiga na tattalin arzikin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Ƙarƙashin nickel yana da muhimmanci a lardin, amma ya fi mayar da hankali ga Morowali, a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar kula da bala'i ta Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an yi girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a birnin Palu da birnin Donggala sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya halaka mutane fiye da 200 a birnin Donggala kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje.
A shekara ta 1996, tsunami ya afka wa yammacin Donggala, inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana kan iyakar tekun Pacific mai girgizar ƙasa kuma tana fuskantar girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu daga cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mafi girma a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin tekun lardin Aceh na arewacin Sumatra ta Indonesiya ta jawo tsunami a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14, kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a yankunan tekun Tekun Indiya, kusan rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A tsakanin ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta girgiza yammacin bakin teku na Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias a bakin tekun Sumatra.
A shekara ta 2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta girgiza tsibirin Java na kudu, wanda shi ne tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya afka wa gabar kudu, wanda ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
A shekara ta 2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta girgiza tsibirin Mentawai da ke gabashin Sumatra kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsayi har zuwa mita 10, wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani karamin girgizar kasa ya girgiza gundumar Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ya jawo lalacewa da firgici, yayin da aka tunatar da mutane game da halakar da girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan lokacin, babu tsunami, amma sama da mutane 100 ne suka mutu a sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
A shekara ta 2018, girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok, wanda ya fi shahara a tsakanin masu yawon buɗe ido a Indonesia, kuma ta kashe mutane fiye da 500.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma dubban masu yawon bude ido sun makale a tsibirin na ɗan lokaci.
