Yanayin ruwan sama na ruwan sama: Yawan ruwan sama a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota ya ragu
Rahoton da Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Dabbobin daji ta Florida ta fitar ya nuna cewa a wasu sassan yankin Tampa Bay, an samu raguwar yawan ruwan damina.
FWC ta ce, a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte, da Collier, akwai yanayi mai tsanani na fure, wanda ke nuna cewa yawan adadin fure yana raguwa.
Wata furen algae mai launin ja tana nisan mil 130 daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin gundumar Lee.
Za a iya samun tabo a wajen mil 10 daga gabar tekun da ke gundumar Hillsborough, amma a wurare da yawa ba a kwatanta da makon da ya gabata ba.
An kuma lura da ruwan sama a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an ba da rahoton matsakaici a cikin ko a gaban tekun Pinellas County, ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a gaban tekun Manatee County, ƙananan taro a cikin ko a gaban tekun Charlotte County, ƙananan taro a cikin ko a gaban tekun Lee County, da ƙananan taro a cikin Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahoton matsalolin numfashi daga Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
A cikin makon da ya gabata, ba a samu wani sabon matsalar numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba.
